Package: libkogboldai-kernel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: KogboldAI Kernel - High-performance narrative generation library
 The KogboldAI Kernel provides optimized C/C++ implementations of AI-assisted
 writing and storytelling primitives using GGML and llama.cpp backends.
 .
 This package contains the shared library.

Package: libkogboldai-kernel-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libkogboldai-kernel (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: KogboldAI Kernel development files
 The KogboldAI Kernel provides optimized C/C++ implementations of AI-assisted
 writing and storytelling primitives using GGML and llama.cpp backends.
 .
 This package contains the header files and development libraries.

Package: python3-kogboldai-kernel
Architecture: any
Depends: libkogboldai-kernel (= ${binary:Version}),
         python3,
         ${python3:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: Python 3 bindings for KogboldAI Kernel
 The KogboldAI Kernel provides optimized C/C++ implementations of AI-assisted
 writing and storytelling primitives using GGML and llama.cpp backends.
 .
 This package contains the Python 3 FFI bindings.
